quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  21,45,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko mi woni jertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndun, si ɓe jertinaama"
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii ɓe seeɗa immorde e Lepte Joomi maa ɗen, maa ɓe wi'a: \"Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, menen men laatinoke tooñuɓe"
  21,47,"Men waɗa manndikirɗe(peesirɗe) Nunɗal ngal fii Ñalnde Darngal hara wonkii woo toñiroytaake hay e huunde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Men adday kun Men yonii Hasbooɓe"
  21,48,Gomɗii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaŋta wonannde hulooɓe ɓen
  21,49,Ɓen hulayɓe Joomi maɓɓe ka wirnii hara kamɓe immorde e Darngal ngal ko ɓe huli
  21,50,"Ndee [Alqur’aanaare] ko nde Jaŋta, ko nde barkinaande Men Jippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yeddayɓe nde"
  21,51,"Gomɗii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Men laatike kadi Annduɓe mo"
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimɓe makko ɓen: \"Ko honɗum woni ɗii nanndonlaaji nate mahiiɗe, ɗin ɗi ufiniɗon e [dewal] mu'un"
  21,53,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Men taw baabiraaɓe amen ɓen no rewde ɗi"
  21,54,"O maaki: \"Gomɗii on laatike onon e baabiraaɓe mon ɓen e nder majjere ɓanngunde wonɗon"
  21,55,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Enee, ko Goonga kan addanɗaa men, kaa an ko e fijooɓe ɓen jeyaɗaa"
  21,56,"Maaku: \"Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin On Taguɗoɗi, min komi jeyaaɗo e seediiɓe ɓen e dow ɗum"
  21,57,"Mi woondirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii ɗii sanamuuji mo'on ɓaawo huccitugol mo'on ko on ruŋii ɓe"